data.description: Welcome to this inviting 3-bed, 2-bath home in Ontario, Oregon! With updated interiors this charming residence is move-in ready. Enjoy a welcoming front porch with a swing and a spacious fenced yard, perfect for outdoor gatherings on the covered deck or under the pergola on the concrete patio. Ample parking for your vehicles and toys with a 2-car carport and a detached 2-car garage with space for hobbies and extra storage. An all new HVAC system was installed in November 2021 for year-round comfort. Located centrally near schools, parks, shops, and dining, this home offers both tranquility and convenience. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! Schedule your showing today.
